  </header>

  <div class="welcome">
    <div id="welcometext">Everything saves automatically — you can close this and come back anytime.</div>
    <div class="settings">
      <select class="mini" id="structureSel" title="Your business structure — this changes which entity documents you need" aria-label="Business structure">
        <option value="single-llc">Single-member LLC</option>
