      </select>
      <button class="mini" id="privatebtn">🔒 Make private</button>
      <button class="mini" id="printbtn">🖨️ Print</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- NEXT STEP -->
  <div class="nextstep" id="nextstep"></div>

  <!-- CONTROLS -->
  <div class="controls">
    <div class="toggle on" id="focusToggle"><span class="sw"></span><span>Focus mode — show only what's next</span></div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <button class="lnk reset" id="reset">Reset statuses</button>
  </div>

  <div class="legend">
    <span><span class="dot need"></span>Not started</span>
    <span><span class="dot prog"></span>In progress</span>
    <span><span class="dot have"></span>Done</span>
    <span style="color:#b3aec2">· tap a chip to move it along</span>
  </div>

  <div id="tracks"></div>

  <!-- RESOURCES -->
  <div class="res">
    <h3>📎 Your documents &amp; links</h3>
    <div class="rhint">Everything you need, in one place. The guides below are the ones we've been working from.</div>
    <div class="rsub">Do it online</div>
    <div class="resgrid">
      <a href="https://eva.virginia.gov/register-now.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">🟢</span><span>Register in eVA<small>Start Step 1 here</small></span></a>
      <a href="https://certification-app.sbsd.virginia.gov/boLogin" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📝</span><span>SWaM application portal<small>Start Step 2 here</small></span></a>
      <a href="https://cis.scc.virginia.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">🏛️</span><span>Virginia SCC (CIS)<small>Download your Articles of Organization</small></span></a>
      <a href="https://www.sbsd.virginia.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📍</span><span>SBSD — check status<small>After you submit</small></span></a>
      <a href="https://eva.virginia.gov/get-help-customer-care.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">☎️</span><span>eVA Customer Care<small>Stuck? Real people help</small></span></a>
      <a href="https://www.irs.gov/businesses/small-businesses-self-employed/get-an-employer-identification-number" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">🔢</span><span>IRS EIN<small>Look up / retrieve your EIN letter</small></span></a>
    </div>
    <div class="rsub">The guides we shared</div>
    <div class="resgrid">
      <a href="SacredVibes_Tracker_Assets/eVA_SWaM_Certification_Presentation.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📄</span><span>eVA &amp; SWaM walkthrough deck<small>The full workshop slides</small></span></a>
      <a href="SacredVibes_Tracker_Assets/Capability_Statement_Fact_Sheet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📄</span><span>Capability Statement fact sheet<small>What goes on your 1-pager</small></span></a>
      <a href="SacredVibes_Tracker_Assets/Capabilities_Statement_Template_2025.docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📝</span><span>Capability Statement template<small>Fill-in-the-blanks (Word)</small></span></a>
      <a href="SacredVibes_Tracker_Assets/Virginia_Business_Resource_Guide.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📕</span><span>Virginia Business Resource Guide<small>The big handbook, for reference</small></span></a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="foot">
    <b>GlowStrm, LLC</b> — Strategic communications · <i>What grows, glows.</i><br>
    Built for Sacred Vibes Healing &amp; Wellness from the Virginia SBSD "Big Opportunities, Bold Partnerships" workshop. A readiness guide, not legal advice — confirm current requirements at <b>sbsd.virginia.gov</b>. Your entries stay in this browser, on this device only.
  </div>
</div>

